  "prompt": "How can I arrange a personal counselling session with Tanmoy Ray?",
  "response": "To arrange a personal counseling session with Tanmoy Ray, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. **Visit His Website**: Go to Tanmoy Ray's official website where he typically provides details about his counseling services.\n\n2. **Fill Out a Contact Form**: Look for a contact form on his website. Fill in your details such as your name, email address, phone number, and any specific requirements or questions you might have.\n\n3. **Email Inquiry**: You can also send an email directly to the provided email address on his website. Be sure to include your background information, the purpose of seeking counseling, and your availability.\n\n4. **Social Media**: Tanmoy Ray is active on various social media platforms. You can reach out to him via LinkedIn, Twitter, or other social media channels where he might have professional profiles.\n\n5. **Booking Platforms**: He might be registered on professional counseling or coaching platforms where you can directly book a session.\n\n6. **Referrals and Networking**: If you are part of educational or professional networks, you might find referrals or contacts who can help you arrange a session.\n\nHere is a sample email you might send:\n\n**Subject**: Request for Personal Counseling Session\n\n**Body**:\n\nDear Mr. Ray,\n\nI hope this message finds you well. My name is [Your Name], and I am [briefly mention your background, e.g., a student, professional, etc.]. I am reaching out to inquire about arranging a personal counseling session with you to discuss [mention the specific topic or issue, e.g., career guidance, higher education, etc.].\n\nCould you please provide information on how to proceed with booking a session? Additionally, I would appreciate it if you could share any details regarding scheduling, fees, and preparation required from my side.\n\nThank you for your time and assistance. I look forward to your response.\n\nBest regards,  \n[Your Full Name]  \n[Your Contact Information]\n\nMake sure to check his website or social media for any specific instructions or updated contact details.",
